                    </div>

                    <!-- Introduction -->
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        Manila, the capital of the Philippines, is a densely populated bayside city with a rich and complex history. It is a city of contrasts, blending Spanish colonial architecture with modern skyscrapers. Its heart is the walled city of **Intramuros**, the historic core founded by the Spanish in the 16th century. Manila is the country's economic, political, social, and educational center.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Key Information Table -->
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10">
